quran[36]{c,v,t}:
  26,192,Soni chisimu jele (Qur’aniji) jiŵele jakutulusyidwa kuumila kwa M’mbuje jwa iwumbe yosope
  26,193,Watulwiche najo Nsiimu (Jibulilu) wakulupichika
  26,194,"Pantima penu (mmwe Muhammadi ﷺ), kuti m’be mwa akutetela"
  26,195,Mu chiŵecheto cha Charabu chakupikanika chenene
  26,196,Soni yalakweyi yili mu itabu ya (ŵandu) ŵandanda
  26,197,Ana nganichiŵa chilosyo kukwao chanti ŵalijiganye ŵa ŵanache ŵa Israila (mpela Abdullah bin Salâm ŵaŵaujitiche Usilamu) ni kujimanya jalakwe (Qur’aniji kuti jakuona)
  26,198,Soni tungajitulusye (Qur’aniji) kwa ŵanepe ŵangaŵa ŵarabu
  26,199,"Basi ni kujisooma kukwao, nga nganaŵa ŵakujikulupilila jalakwe"
  26,200,Iyyoyopeyo tukupitisye (kujikanila Qur’an) m’mitima mwa akuleŵa (atamose kuti jukwasoomela mwarabu n’jao)
  26,201,Ngaajikulupilila jalakwe mpaka akaiwone ilagasyo yakupoteka nnope
  26,202,Basi ni tiichaichilila mwachisupuchisya ŵanganyao akakumanyilila
  26,203,"Ni tachiti: “Ana uwwe ngakomboleka kupedwa lipesa (kuti tutende toba)?”"
  26,204,Ana akuijanguya ilagasyo Yetu
  26,205,"Ana nkuiona uli, naga tuli twasengwasisye ŵanganyao kwa yaka (yejinji)"
  26,206,Kaneka ni kwaichilila (ipotesi) yaŵaliji nkupedwa chilanga
  26,207,Ngasiyakamuchisya ayila yaŵele ali nkusengwasyidwa nayo
  26,208,Soni Uwwe nganituujonanjeje musi uliose ikaŵeje wakolaga akutetela
  26,209,"Kuŵa chikumbusyo, soni Uwwe nganituŵa ŵalupuso (pakwajonanga ŵandu nkanitwatetele)"
  26,210,Soni mashetani ngaŵa ni gagatulwisye jalakwe (Qur’aniji mwaakuŵechetela achimakafili)
  26,211,"Soni ngaikuŵajilwa kukwao, nambo soni nganaŵa akombwele (kujitulusya)"
  26,212,Chisimu ŵanganyao yakupikanila (Qur’an kumawunde jichitulukaga) asiŵiiliidwe
  26,213,"Basi ngasimunnumbanjila pampepe ni Allah nnungu jwine, ntakwika mum’bele mwa akulagasyidwa"
  26,214,Ni mwatetelani ŵalukosyo lwenu ŵali ŵakuŵandichila
  26,215,Nimwagoyechesye lipapiko lyenu (lya chanasa) aŵala ŵankuyiye mwa ŵakulupilila
  26,216,"Sano naga akunnyosya basi jilani: “Chisimu une mambalene nayo ichindu yankutenda.”"
  26,217,"Nin’jegamile kwa (Allah) Jwamachili gakupunda, Jwachanasa channope"
  26,218,Ajula jwaakum’bona ndema jankwima (jikape kuswali patahajjudi)
  26,219,Ni kutenganyikatenganyika kwenu (pakuswali ipindi nsano) pamo ni akusujudu (akuswali ŵane)
  26,220,"Chisimu Jwalakwe ni Jwakupikanichisya, Jwakumanyilila nnope"
  26,221,Ana nantagulile ŵanganyammwe jwagakuntuluchilaga mashetani
  26,222,"Gakuntuluchilaga jwalijose jwaunami wejinji, jwasambi nnope"
  26,223,Gakuponyaga yagapikene (kwinani kwaponyela achibimbi) nambo ŵajinji mwa ŵanganyao ŵaunami
  26,224,Akwimba chilaanga ŵaliose akasaŵakuyaga ŵasokonechele
  26,225,Ana ngankuiona yanti ŵanganyao m’chiŵata chilichose (chamaloŵe) akuŵa nkupojola
  26,226,Soni kuti ŵanganyao akasaŵechetaga yangakutendaga
  26,227,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, ni kunkolangaga Allah kwejinji, ni kulikulupusya achimisyene panyuma pakutendeledwa lupuso (pakwajanga achimakafili ni ilaanga pa ilaanga yao yaakwimba yakwagamba Asilamu). Sano pangakaŵapa tamanyilile aŵala ŵatesile lupuso kwagalauchila kutagalauchile"